<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay frames="40" />
名為釣魚大會的戰爭，<delay20 />
就要在<tag a="110" b="8" /><delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />展開了呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你想問對手是誰？<10_4 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對手不是別人，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正是你自己啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />最近利用假資訊引起他人的注意，<delay20 />
再透過對方的反應取樂的行為，<delay20 />
好像也被稱為「釣魚」呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們不能被表面的假象所迷惑，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要釣<delay8 />就應該去釣真正的魚才對吧！？<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所謂的釣魚，<delay20 />
就像談戀愛時的應對進退一樣！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當魚兒稍微被你吸引住的時候，<delay20 />
不應該急著馬上收線，<delay20 />
而是要靜觀其變<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要耐心等待，<delay20 />
等到魚兒也變得難捨難分，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是該收線的時候！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯，就像談戀愛一樣<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也會有失敗的時候就是了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈～！</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />參加釣魚大會時，<delay20 />
得在時間限制內釣到越多條魚越好！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也就是說，<delay8 />
就算帶著一大堆事先釣到的魚來參加，<delay20 />
也是沒有意義的喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果想參加釣魚大會的話，<delay20 />
只要去廣場<delay8 />找<colour id="3" />俞司廷<colour id="65535" />說話就行了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />我嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就不參加了。<delay20 />
我可不想讓自己的雙手沾滿魚腥味，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>